2) cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper presents a new approach to the analysis and design of consensus protocols, which is related to the field of systems and control. 
3) cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper deals with multi-agent systems and their consensus behavior, which falls under the category of multiagent systems. 
4) cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper uses graph signal processing techniques, which are often used in the field of neural and evolutionary computing. 
5) cs.SP (Signal Processing) - The paper presents a new approach to consensus analysis and design using graph spectrum filters, which is related to the field of signal processing.
